{"tid":2461733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安局澄清：李局長皮膚現紅是皮膚手術的過渡反應 沒有與疫苗有關的不良反應或不適","createTime":"2021-03-25T14:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T14:25:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"62dd373a582918ca525d33a2a5d5fceabacc2332","tid":2461733,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"保安局回應傳媒查詢保安局局長身體狀況<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  回應傳媒查詢保安局局長李家超的身體狀況，保安局發言人今日（三月二十五日）表示，保安局局長接種第二劑新冠疫苗後，完全沒有任何不良反應或不適，每日如常工作，並沒有休假。<br />\n<br />\n  保安局局長較早前經私家醫生進行了頸部扁平疣皮膚手術，皮膚現紅是手術後的過渡期反應，這與今日到伊利沙伯醫院作一般例行覆診無關。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年3月25日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間21時54分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/25/P2021032500800.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202103%2F25%2FP2021032500800.htm&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=ea0a7035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/25/P2021032500800.htm</a>"},{"pid":"419acdd2081ab9ee3ba6b0b14188760a63be8b21","tid":2461733,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"出埋政府新聞稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e05248df639d7964ae7138cd41f5d96a655825","tid":2461733,"uid":124623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"搞咩搞到生上頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b33a14756b3eb4d09eceb64fdaccec7fbabd21","tid":2461733,"uid":271485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"割包皮算唔算皮膚手術？"},{"pid":"64a2c0911c5a4182e0793169ff0d5e7b0092cdcd","tid":2461733,"uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"Officially denied <br />\n可以信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e694be68fa40f